high_descs: Remove white mug from coffee maker.
Turn around, proceed to wall.  Turn left, proceed to microwave.
Open microwave, put mug in, close door.  Wait five seconds, open door.  Remove mug, close door.
Face up to cabinet above microwave.
Open cabinet, place mug in, close cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Heat up mug, put mug in cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the right, and the right again to find the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Carry the mug and turn around, then to the left to locate the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the mug inside. Shut the door and turn it on. Open the door and take mug out, then shut the door.
Hold the mug and look above the microwave.
Open the right cabinet and place the mug inside, then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat a mug then put it away in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the coffee maker
Grab the mug out of the coffee maker
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave and then take it out
Look up at the cabinets above the microwave
Put the mug in the cabinet on the right
anns.task_desc: Putting a mug in a cabinet
